<h2>Typeface</h2>

<p>Public Sans is the only font to be used by agencies for NSW Government websites and online applications. Major headings through to body copy must also use Public Sans.</p>

<p>Public Sans is a free font and available from <a href="https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Public+Sans" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Fonts</a>.</p>

