<h3>System fonts</h3>
<p>System fonts are rendered locally by your web browser, this provides greater speed when loading your content. The preferred system font is Arial.</p>

<p>As a good rule of thumb, you should still refer to a system font as a fallback in your CSS font stack:</p>
<p><code>body {font-family: 'Public Sans', Arial, sans-serif; }</code></p>


