<h2 class="nsw-h3">Basic typography</h2>
<p>A wrapper class of <code>nsw-body-content</code> applies styles for basic typographic elements</p>
{{#>_docs-example simple="true" separated="true"}}
  <div class="nsw-body-content">
    <h2>This is a sample heading</h2>
    <hr/>
    <p>Nunc porta purus non sem laoreet eleifend a pharetra ex.</p>
    <blockquote>
      “Pellentesque facilisis sed quam id blandit. Class aptent taciti sociosqu ad litora torquent per conubia nostra, per inceptos himenaeos.”
      <cite>Nullam faucibus</cite>
    </blockquote>
  </div>
{{/_docs-example}}
